    "description_long": "This is a sleek, low-profile sports car with a metallic purple exterior and a streamlined, aerodynamic body. The car features a long hood, aggressive front grille with three prominent lights, and a slightly raised rear with a subtle integrated spoiler. The side windows are tinted, and the roofline slopes smoothly towards the rear, giving it a classic fastback silhouette. Chrome accents are visible on the wheels and side mirrors, while the wheels themselves are large, multi-spoke alloys. The interior, partially visible through the windows, includes a tan steering wheel and dark dashboard, suggesting a focus on both style and performance.",
